Atunṣe silẹ tun mu ṣiṣẹda Atunṣe ṣiṣẹ','Email designated Publishers when a %s is submitted'=>'Imeeli awọn Onkọwe ti a yan nigbati a ba fi %s silẹ','Email designated Publishers when a %s is published'=>'Imeeli awọn Onkọwe ti a yan nigbati a ba tẹ %s jade','Email designated Publishers when a %s is approved'=>'Imeeli awọn Onkọwe ti a yan nigbati a ba fọwọsi %s','Email Editors and Administrators when a %s is submitted'=>'Imeeli awọn Olutayo ati awọn Alakoso nigbati a ba fi %s silẹ','Email Editors and Administrators when a %s is published'=>'Imeeli awọn Olutayo ati awọn Alakoso nigbati a ba tẹ %s jade','Email Editors and Administrators when a %s is approved'=>'Imeeli awọn Olutayo ati awọn Alakoso nigbati a ba fọwọsi %s','PublishPress Revisions Site Settings'=>'Iṣeto Aaye Atunṣe PublishPress','These are the default settings for options which can be adjusted per-site.'=>'Eyi ni awọn eto aiyipada fun awọn aṣayan ti a le ṣe atunṣe fun ọkọọkan aaye.','Use this tab to make NETWORK-WIDE changes to PublishPress Revisions settings. %s'=>'Lo taabu yii lati ṣe awọn ayipada ni gbogbo NETWORK si awọn eto PublishPress Revisions. %s','You can also specify %1$sdefaults for site-specific settings%2$s.'=>'O tun le ṣalaye %1$s awọn aiyipada fun awọn eto aaye pataki %2$s.','Here you can change the default value for settings which are controlled separately on each site.'=>'Nibi o le yipada iye aiyipada fun awọn eto ti a ṣakoso ni iyasọtọ lori ọkọọkan aaye.','Note that %1$s network-wide settings%2$s may also be available.'=>'Ṣe akiyesi pe %1$s awọn eto ni gbogbo nẹtiwọọki %2$s le tun wa.','License'=>'Iwe-aṣẹ','Past Revisions are earlier versions of a post.'=>'Awọn Atunṣe ti o kọja jẹ awọn ẹya iṣaaju ti ifiweranṣẹ kan.','This post type does not support Past Revisions.'=>'Iru ifiweranṣẹ yii ko ni atilẹyin awọn Atunṣe ti o kọja.','New Revisions are changes which are not yet published.'=>'Awọn Atunṣe Tuntun jẹ awọn ayipada ti ko ti gbejade.','Note: Third party code may cause some post types to be incompatible with PublishPress Revisions.'=>'Akíyèsí: Koodu ẹgbẹ kẹta le fa diẹ ninu awọn iru ifiweranṣẹ lati jẹ alailẹgbẹ pẹlu PublishPress Revisions.','For Revisions integration on the Content Calendar, Overview and Content Board, please update %sPublishPress Planner Pro%s.'=>'Fun iṣọpọ Atunṣe lori Kalendaru Akoonu, Akopọ ati Igbimọ Akoonu, jọwọ ṣe imudojuiwọn %sPublishPress Planner Pro%s.','Ready to enhance your revision workflow?'=>'Ṣe o setan lati mu ilọsiwaju iṣẹ ṣiṣe atunṣe rẹ pọ si?','Get PublishPress Statuses Pro and optimize your revision process with custom revision statuses.'=>'Gba PublishPress Statuses Pro ki o mu ilana atunṣe rẹ ṣiṣẹ pẹlu awọn ipo atunṣe aṣa.','Define your own statuses before or after Revision Submitted'=>'Ṣe apejuwe awọn ipo tirẹ ṣaaju tabi lẹhin Atunṣe ti a fi silẹ','New predefined statuses: Deferred, Needs Work, Rejected'=>'Awọn ipo ti a ti ṣeto tẹlẹ: Ti a dawọ, Nilo Iṣẹ, Ti kọ','Statuses can be specific to a post type'=>'Awọn ipo le jẹ pataki si iru ifiweranṣẹ kan','Control access to statuses per-role'=>'Ṣakoso wiwọle si awọn ipo ni ibamu si ipa','Status workflow can be nested with sub-statuses'=>'Ilana iṣẹ ipo le jẹ ti a fi sinu pẹlu awọn ipo abẹ','Get PublishPress Statuses Pro'=>'Gba PublishPress Statuses Pro','Learn More'=>'Kọ ẹkọ diẹ sii','Pro Plugin'=>'Pro Plugin','Install Statuses Pro to unlock custom revision statuses.'=>'Fi Statuses Pro sinu lati ṣii awọn ipo atunyẹwo adani.','Configure for any post type and role to match your editing workflow.'=>'Ṣeto fun iru ifiweranṣẹ eyikeyi ati ipa lati ba iṣẹ ṣiṣatunkọ rẹ mu.','Get Statuses Pro'=>'Gba Statuses Pro','Maximum revisions per post:'=>'Iye to pọ julọ ti awọn atunyẹwo fun ifiweranṣẹ:','(unlimited)'=>'(aimuṣẹ)','Note that archiving can also be disabled by %1$sPost Type%2$s.'=>'Ṣe akiyesi pe a tun le pa ifiṣura mọ nipasẹ %1$sPost Type%2$s.','%s capability'=>'%s agbara','Assign capability to roles'=>'Yan agbara fun awọn ipa','Prevent non-Administrators from restoring a revision without the %s.'=>'Dena awọn ti kii ṣe Alakoso lati tun pada si atunyẹwo laisi %s.','Prevent non-Administrators from restoring a revision without the restore_revisions capability'=>'Dena awọn ti kii ṣe Alakoso lati tun pada si atunyẹwo laisi agbara restore_revisions','Modification Date'=>'Ọjọ Ayipada','Revision Creation'=>'Ṣiṣẹda Atunyẹwo','Submission'=>'Ifisilẹ','Scheduling'=>'Iṣeto','Publication'=>'Iwe atẹjade','Management'=>'Isakoso','Create Revision capabilities'=>'Ṣẹda awọn agbara Atunyẹwo','Assign capabilities to roles'=>'Yan awọn agbara fun awọn ipa','If the user can\'t edit the published post, require %s.'=>'Ti olumulo ko ba le ṣe atunṣe ifiweranṣẹ ti a tẹjade, nilo %s.','If the user can\'t edit the published post, require Create Revision capabilities (copy_posts, copy_others_pages, etc.)'=>'Ti olumulo ko ba le ṣe atunṣe ifiweranṣẹ ti a tẹjade, beere awọn agbara Ṣẹda Atunṣe (copy_posts, copy_others_pages, ati bẹbẹ lọ)','To expand the Pages list, assign %s.'=>'Lati fa akojọ Awọn Oju-iwe pọ, yan %s.','Listing capabilities'=>'Awọn agbara atokọ','To expand the Pages list, assign Listing capabilities (list_others_pages, list_published_posts, etc.)'=>'Lati fa akojọ Awọn Oju-iwe pọ, yan Awọn agbara atokọ (list_others_pages, list_published_posts, ati bẹbẹ lọ)','This plugin introduces a new user role, "Revisor."'=>'Ẹya yii n mu ipa olumulo tuntun wa, "Revisor."','Revision by a user who does not have the %s will cause all custom html tags to be stripped out.'=>'Atunṣe nipasẹ olumulo ti ko ni %s yoo fa ki gbogbo awọn aami html aṣa rọrun jade.','Revision by a user who does not have the unfiltered_html capability will cause all custom html tags to be stripped out.'=>'Atunṣe nipasẹ olumulo ti ko ni agbara unfiltered_html yoo fa ki gbogbo awọn aami html aṣa rọrun jade.','Broadest compat including Elementor, Divi, Beaver Builder'=>'Ibamu julo pẹlu Elementor, Divi, Beaver Builder','Standard storage schema for broadest 3rd party compat'=>'Iwe afọwọkọ ibi ipamọ boṣewa fun ibamu 3rd party julo','Enhanced Revision access control with PublishPress plugins'=>'Iṣakoso iraye si Atunṣe ti a ti ni ilọsiwaju pẹlu awọn afikun PublishPress','In enhanced mode, a Revision\'s status is stored by standard WordPress schema. Some plugins are incompatible.'=>'Ni ipo ti a ti ni ilọsiwaju, ipo Atunṣe kan ni a tọju nipasẹ iwe afọwọkọ WordPress boṣewa. Diẹ ninu awọn afikun ko ni ibamu.','Prevent Revision creation if the post already has another Revision in progress.'=>'Dena ṣẹda Atunṣe ti ifiweranṣẹ naa ti ni Atunṣe miiran ti n lọ.','Work around cache plugin conflicts by requerying for revisions before suppressing the New Revision link.'=>'Jẹ ki o ṣiṣẹ ni ayika awọn ariyanjiyan afikun kaṣe nipa tun beere fun awọn atunṣe ṣaaju ki o to pa ọna asopọ Atunṣe Tuntun.','If the user does not have a regular Edit link, recaption the %s link as "Edit."'=>'Ti olumulo ko ba ni ọna asopọ Ẹditi deede, yi %s ọna asopọ pada si "Ẹditi."','Default labels are "Not Submitted for Approval", "Submitted for Approval", "Scheduled Revision"'=>'Awọn aami aiyipada ni "Ko ti fi silẹ fun Ijẹrisi", "Ti fi silẹ fun Ijẹrisi", "Atunṣe ti a ti ṣeto"','Enable published content to be copied, edited, submitted for approval and managed on the %sNew Revisions%s screen.'=>'Mu ki akoonu ti a tẹjade le jẹ ẹda, ṣiṣatunkọ, fi silẹ fun ijẹrisi ati ṣakoso lori iboju %sAtunṣe Tuntun%s.','Submit Revision capabilities'=>'Fi Iṣẹ Atunṣe silẹ','If the user can\'t edit the published post, require Submit Revision capabilities (revise_posts, revise_others_pages, etc.)'=>'Ti olumulo ko ba le ṣe atunṣe ifiweranṣẹ ti a tẹjade, beere awọn agbara Fi Atunṣe silẹ (revise_posts, revise_others_pages, ati bẹbẹ lọ)','When a %s is published, update post publish date to current time.'=>'Nigbati a ba tẹjade %s, ṣe imudojuiwọn ọjọ atẹjade ifiweranṣẹ si akoko lọwọlọwọ.','When a %s is published, update post modified date to current time.'=>'Nigbati a ba tẹjade %s, ṣe imudojuiwọn ọjọ ti a ṣe atunṣe ifiweranṣẹ si akoko lọwọlọwọ.','When a new revision is created by any user who is allowed to submit revisions, automatically submit it.'=>'Nigbati a ba ṣẹda atunṣe tuntun nipasẹ eyikeyi olumulo ti o ni ẹtọ lati fi awọn atunṣe silẹ, fi silẹ laifọwọyi.','Auto-submit revisions if the user can directly edit the main post.'=>'Fi awọn atunṣe silẹ laifọwọyi ti olumulo ba le ṣe atunṣe ifiweranṣẹ akọkọ taara.','This allows immediate approval within the Compare screen. If disabled, a Preview link is provided instead.'=>'Eyi gba aṣẹ lẹsẹkẹsẹ laarin iboju Afiwe. Ti a ko ba mu ṣiṣẹ, ọna asopọ Ifihan ni a pese dipo.','If a currently published post or page is edited and a future date set, the change will not be applied until the selected date.'=>'Ti a ba ṣe atunṣe ifiweranṣẹ tabi oju-iwe ti a tẹjade lọwọlọwọ ati pe ọjọ iwaju ti ṣeto, iyipada ko ni lo titi di ọjọ ti a ti yan.','Publish scheduled revisions using the WP-Cron mechanism. On some sites, publication will fail if this setting is disabled.'=>'Ṣe atẹjade awọn atunṣe ti a ṣeto akoko nipa lilo ẹrọ WP-Cron. Ni diẹ ninu awọn aaye, atẹjade yoo kuna ti a ko ba mu iṣeto yii ṣiṣẹ.','Publish scheduled revisions asynchronously, via a secondary http request from the server.  This is usually best since it eliminates delay, but some servers may not support it.'=>'Ṣe atẹjade awọn atunṣe ti a ṣeto akoko ni aiyipada, nipasẹ ibeere http keji lati ọdọ olupin. Eyi jẹ ti o dara julọ nigbagbogbo nitori o yọkuro idaduro, ṣugbọn diẹ ninu awọn olupin le ma ṣe atilẹyin rẹ.','The WP-Cron trigger is disabled, but scheduled tasks are still excecuted using a custom trigger.'=>'Ipa WP-Cron ti wa ni pa, ṣugbọn awọn iṣẹ ti a ṣeto akoko ṣi n ṣiṣẹ pẹlu ipa aṣa kan.','Caption the button as either "Approve and Publish" or "Approve and Schedule."'=>'Pe bọtini naa bi "Fọwọsi ati Ṣe atẹjade" tabi "Fọwọsi ati Ṣeto."','This may improve compatibility with some plugins.'=>'Eyi le mu ibamu pọ si pẹlu diẹ ninu awọn afikun.','Control New Revisions access with the %s.'=>'Ṣakoso iraye si Awọn Atunṣe Tuntun pẹlu %s.','Control New Revisions access with the manage_revision_queue capability.'=>'Ṣakoso iraye si Awọn Atunṣe Tuntun pẹlu agbara manage_revision_queue.','Users will need the %s to edit others\' Unsubmitted Revisions.'=>'Awọn olumulo yoo nilo %s lati ṣe atunṣe Awọn Atunṣe ti a ko fi silẹ ti awọn miiran.','Users will need the manage_unsubmitted_revisions capability to edit others\' Unsubmitted Revisions.'=>'Awọn olumulo yoo nilo agbara manage_unsubmitted_revisions lati ṣe atunṣe Awọn Atunṣe ti a ko fi silẹ ti awọn miiran.','If the user can\'t edit the published post, require the %s.'=>'Ti olumulo ko ba le ṣe atunṣe ifiweranṣẹ ti a tẹjade, beere %s.','If the user can\'t edit the published post, require the edit_others_revisions capability.'=>'Ti olumulo ko ba le ṣe atunṣe ifiweranṣẹ ti a tẹjade, beere agbara edit_others_revisions.','If the user can\'t edit the published post, require the list_others_revisions capability.'=>'Ti olumulo ko ba le ṣe atunṣe ifiweranṣẹ ti a tẹjade, beere agbara list_others_revisions.','Bypass the above restrictions for others\' revisions to logged in user\'s own posts.'=>'Gba awọn ihamọ loke fun awọn atunṣe ti awọn miiran si awọn ifiweranṣẹ tirẹ ti olumulo ti o wọle.','Regenerate "post has revision" flags'=>'Tun ṣe agbekalẹ "ifiranṣẹ ni atunṣe" awọn asia','Apply this maintenance operation if Has Revision labels on Posts / Pages screens mismatch the New Revisions listing.'=>'Lo iṣẹ itọju yii ti awọn afi Has Revision lori awọn iboju Ifiweranṣẹ / Awọn Oju-iwe ko baamu pẹlu atokọ Awọn Atunṣe Tuntun.','For enhanced notifications, install %sPublishPress Planner%s.'=>'Fun awọn iwifunni ti a ti ni ilọsiwaju, fi sori ẹrọ %sPublishPress Planner%s.','For enhanced notifications, update %sPublishPress Planner%s.'=>'Fun awọn iwifunni ti a ti mu ilọsiwaju, ṣe imudojuiwọn %sPublishPress Planner%s.','Send revision action notifications using the customizable %1$sPublishPress Planner Notifications system%2$s.'=>'Ran awọn iwifunni iṣatunṣe lọwọlọwọ nipa lilo %1$sPublishPress Planner Notifications system%2$s ti a le ṣe adani.','Upgrade to Revisions Pro to send revision action notifications using the customizable %1$sPublishPress Planner Notifications system%2$s.'=>'Gbadun si Revisions Pro lati ran awọn iwifunni iṣatunṣe lọwọlọwọ nipa lilo %1$sPublishPress Planner Notifications system%2$s ti a le ṣe adani.','Users matching Planner > Notifications configuration get revision notifications only if they can edit the published post.'=>'Awọn olumulo ti o baamu eto Planner > Notifications gba awọn iwifunni iṣatunṣe nikan ti wọn ba le ṣe atunṣe ifiweranṣẹ ti a tẹjade.','Never'=>'Ko si','By default'=>'Nipa aiyipada','Always'=>'Nigbagbogbo','select recipients'=>'yan awọn olugba','To avoid notification failures, buffer emails for delayed sending once minute, hour or day limits are exceeded'=>'Lati yago fun ikuna iwifunni, pa awọn imeeli fun gbigbe pẹ ti o ba ti kọja awọn aala iṣẹju kan, wakati kan tabi ọjọ kan','Notification Buffer'=>'Ibufe Iwifunni','Notification Log'=>'Iwe Itan Iwifunni','Purge Notification Buffer'=>'Pa Ibufe Iwifunni','Truncate Notification Log'=>'Dinku Iwe Itan Iwifunni','Sent in last minute: %d / %d'=>'Ti a ran ni iṣẹju to kẹhin: %d / %d','Sent in last hour: %d / %d'=>'Ti a ran ni wakati to kẹhin: %d / %d','Sent in last day: %d / %d'=>'Ti a ran ni ọjọ to kẹhin: %d / %d','Seconds until next buffer processing time: %d'=>'Awọn aaya titi de akoko ṣiṣe ibufe ti nbọ: %d','Show Notification Log / Buffer'=>'Fihan Iwe Itan Iwifunni / Ibufe','Show with message content'=>'Fihan pẹlu akoonu ifiranṣẹ','Ready to enhance your revision notifications?'=>'Ṣe o setan lati mu ilọsiwaju awọn iwifunni iṣatunṣe rẹ?','Upgrade to Revisions Pro for integration with our PublishPress Planner Notifications framework.'=>'Gba imudojuiwọn si Revisions Pro fun isopọ pẹlu ilana PublishPress Planner Notifications wa.','Customize notification message and subject'=>'Ṣe adani ifiranṣẹ ikilọ ati akọle','Notify for a specific post type, category or term'=>'Bẹwẹ fun iru ifiweranṣẹ kan, ẹka tabi ọrọ','Target specific roles, users, or user groups'=>'Fojusi awọn ipa pato, awọn olumulo, tabi awọn ẹgbẹ olumulo','With PublishPress Planner Pro, send notifications to a Slack channel'=>'Pẹlu PublishPress Planner Pro, firanṣẹ awọn ikilọ si ikanni Slack','Pro Feature'=>'Ẹya Pro','Upgrade to Revisions Pro to unlock Planner Notifications integration.'=>'Gba imudojuiwọn si Revisions Pro lati ṣii isopọ Planner Notifications.','Customize notification content and recipients for each notification type.'=>'Ṣe adani akoonu ikilọ ati awọn olugba fun ọkọọkan iru ikilọ.','Some themes may block revision preview.'=>'Diẹ ninu awọn akọle le pa aiyipada atunṣe.','Published Post Slug'=>'Pẹlu Post Slug','Revision Slug'=>'Atunṣe Slug','Revision ID only'=>'Atunṣe ID nikan','Some themes or plugins may require Revision Slug or Revision ID link type for proper template loading and field display.'=>'Diẹ ninu awọn akọle tabi awọn afikun le nilo Atunṣe Slug tabi Atunṣe ID iru ọna asopọ fun ikojọpọ awoṣe to tọ ati ifihan aaye.','The revision preview argument is configured by constant definition: %s'=>'Iṣeduro aiyipada atunṣe ti wa ni iṣeto nipasẹ itumọ iduro: %s','Adjust preview links to use "rv_preview" argument instead of "preview". Experiment to see which works best with your theme.'=>'Ṣatunṣe awọn ọna asopọ aiyipada lati lo "rv_preview" aiyipada dipo "preview". Ṣe idanwo lati rii eyi ti o dara julọ pẹlu akọle rẹ.','Some themes may require this setting for correct revision preview display.'=>'Diẹ ninu awọn akọle le nilo iṣeto yii fun ifihan aiyipada atunṣe to tọ.','This should usually be enabled, except to work around conflicts with other another plugin\'s postmeta data.'=>'Eyi yẹ ki o jẹ igbagbogbo mu ṣiṣẹ, ayafi lati ṣiṣẹ ni ayika awọn ariyanjiyan pẹlu data postmeta ti afikun miiran.','If the user can\'t publish, require the %s to edit others\' unpublished Posts.'=>'Ti olumulo ko ba le gbejade, beere %s lati ṣatunkọ awọn Ifiweranṣẹ ti ko gbejade ti awọn miiran.','If the user can\'t publish, require the edit_others_drafts capability to edit others\' unpublished Posts.'=>'Ti olumulo ko ba le gbejade, beere agbara edit_others_drafts lati ṣatunkọ awọn Ifiweranṣẹ ti ko gbejade ti awọn miiran.','If post-specific permissions restrict or expand access to a post, apply those permissions to its revisions also.'=>'Ti awọn igbanilaaye pato post ba ni ihamọ tabi fa iraye si si ifiweranṣẹ, lo awọn igbanilaaye wọnyẹn si awọn atunṣe rẹ paapaa.','Rank Math SEO may prevent Revision update on some sites.'=>'Rank Math SEO le dena imudojuiwọn Atunse lori diẹ ninu awọn aaye.','WPML Translation Management'=>'WPML Itumọ Isakoso','Sync "Needs Update" flags'=>'Sopọ "N nilo imudojuiwọn" awọn asia','Set "Needs Update" for any post with translations which was updated (possibly by revision approval) more recently than its translations.'=>'Ṣeto "N nilo imudojuiwọn" fun eyikeyi ifiweranṣẹ pẹlu awọn itumọ ti a ti imudojuiwọn (o ṣee ṣe nipasẹ ifọwọsi atunse) laipẹ ju awọn itumọ rẹ lọ.','Show descriptive captions for PublishPress Revisions settings.'=>'Fihan awọn akọle apejuwe fun awọn eto Atunse PublishPress.','Plugin settings, New Revisions contents and related data will be deleted, but only after the last copy of Revisions / Revisions Pro is deleted.'=>'Awọn eto afikun, Awọn akoonu Atunse Tuntun ati data ti o ni ibatan yoo parẹ, ṣugbọn nikan lẹhin ti ẹda ikẹhin ti Atunse / Atunse Pro ti parẹ.','Unlock Pro Integrations'=>'Ṣii Awọn Isopọ Pro','Upgrade to the Pro version for optimal compatibility and prompt, professional support.'=>'Gbigba si ẹya Pro fun ibamu ti o dara julọ ati atilẹyin ọjọgbọn, ni iyara.','Admin'=>'admin','Builder'=>'Builder','Cache'=>'Cache','E-Commerce'=>'E-Commerce','Fields'=>'Fields','Multilingual'=>'Multilingual','SEO'=>'SEO','Workflow'=>'Workflow','Specify which PublishPress Revisions Settings to control network-wide. Unselected settings are controlled separately on each site.'=>'Ṣe alaye eyi ti awọn Eto Atunse PublishPress lati ṣakoso ni gbogbo nẹtiwọọki. Awọn eto ti a ko yan ni a ṣakoso ni ẹka kọọkan lori aaye kọọkan.','network-wide control of "%s"'=>'ìṣakoso nẹtiwọọki ti "%s"','Save Changes'=>'Fipamọ Awọn Ayipada','Revert to Defaults'=>'Pada si Awọn aiyipada','All settings in this form (including those on unselected tabs) will be reset to DEFAULTS.  Are you sure?'=>'Gbogbo eto ni fọọmu yii (pẹlu awọn ti o wa lori awọn taabu ti a ko yan) yoo tunto si DEFAULTS. Ṣe o da ọ loju?','Commerce'=>'Commerce','Multilang'=>'Multilang','Community'=>'Community','Pro'=>'Pro','Supported'=>'Supported','Active Plugin'=>'Active Plugin','Supported by PublishPress Revisions'=>'Ti a ṣe atilẹyin nipasẹ PublishPress Revisions','Supported by Revisions Pro'=>'Ti a ṣe atilẹyin nipasẹ Revisions Pro','Integration Active'=>'Isopọ ti n ṣiṣẹ','Upgrade to Pro to enable this integration'=>'Gbadun si Pro lati mu isopọ yii ṣiṣẹ','Unlock %s integration to enhance your revisions solution.'=>'Tu %s isopọ silẹ lati mu ojutu atunṣe rẹ pọ si.','Active Plugin Integration'=>'Isopọ Plugin ti n ṣiṣẹ','Supported Plugin Integration'=>'Isopọ Plugin ti a ṣe atilẹyin','Supported Plugin'=>'Plugin ti a ṣe atilẹyin','Now'=>'Bayi','Author'=>'Onkọwe','(on approval)'=>'(lori ifọwọsi)','Save changes to continue.'=>'Fipamọ awọn ayipada lati tẹsiwaju.','Please save changes to the revision before submitting it.'=>'Jọwọ fipamọ awọn ayipada si atunṣe ṣaaju ki o to fi silẹ.','Preview this Revision'=>'Ṣe afihan Iwọn yii','View / Publish'=>'Wo / Ṣafihan','View / Approve'=>'Wo / Fọwọsi','View / Moderate saved revision'=>'Wo / Ṣakoso atunṣe ti a fipamọ','View / Submit saved revision'=>'Wo / Fi atunṣe ti a fipamọ silẹ','View unsaved changes'=>'Wo awọn ayipada ti a ko fipamọ','%s%s Revision Edit'=>'%s%s Atunṣe Ṣatunkọ','Revision Submission Error'=>'Aṣiṣe Ifisilẹ Atunṣe','Edit'=>'Ṣatunkọ','Approve and Publish'=>'Fọwọsi ati Ṣafihan','Update in progress...'=>'Nṣiṣẹ imudojuiwọn...','Approve and Schedule'=>'Fọwọsi ati Ṣeto','Update Revisi